[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說光明童子因緣經卷第一",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝奉大",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫試光祿卿傳法大師",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賜紫臣施護奉　詔譯如是我聞：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一時，佛在王舍城，迦蘭陀竹林精舍。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼城中，有一長者，名曰善賢，有大財寶富饒自在，然彼長者，於諸外道尼乾陀等，深生信重。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長者一時，以彼世因緣故，其妻懷妊。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而後一日，世尊於其食時，被袈裟衣，執持應器，入王舍城，次第乞食，漸次至彼善賢長者舍。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼長者，遠見世尊漸近自舍，即謂妻言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今同汝，詣世尊所。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是言已，即與其妻，前詣佛所。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我名善賢，此是我妻，其人懷妊，日月將滿，當所生者，是男？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是女？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝妻胎中，決定是男，其後生已，家族富盛，最上吉祥，現於人中受天勝福，乃至最後，於我法中出家學道，斷諸煩惱，證阿羅漢。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時長者，即取滿鉢上味清淨飲食，奉上世尊。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊受已，作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「願其施者，吉祥安樂。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊言已，持所施食，還復本處。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛去未遠，有一外道，是彼善賢先所重者，見佛世尊已，即作是思惟：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「豈非今時因此沙門瞿曇，長者於我破本信心，我宜往彼詢問其故，沙門瞿曇來何所說？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時彼外道，作是思惟已，即詣長者舍，作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門瞿曇有何願求，來至汝舍？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復作何說？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」長者白言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我師聖者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我妻懷妊故，乃問彼沙門瞿曇，當所生者，是男？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是女？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼謂我言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『定當生男，生已決定家族富盛，最上吉祥，現於人中，受天勝福，乃至最後於我法中，出家學道證阿羅漢。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」而此外道，本善占相，聞是言已，即取白石，施設算法，算量其事為虛為實。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼設算已，具知其事，如佛所言，實無虛妄。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼外道，雖知其實，然作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今若以如實而說，即此長者於彼沙門瞿曇，定生信重，我今宜應語長者言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c27_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『瞿曇所說有實有虛。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0854c28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」時彼外道，作是念已，呼長者妻，近外道前，取左右手，復看手文，及瞻面相。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時善賢長者，即白外道言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我師聖者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先已設算。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故重復看其手文及瞻面相？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」彼外道言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我適算彼瞿曇所說，及相汝妻，審知其事，少分真實，少分虛妄。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」長者復言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何者真實？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者虛妄？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」外道答言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「瞿曇所說汝妻生男，此說是實；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所言生已家族富盛，此亦是實。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然子生時，合有少分火光明事，此子後必壞汝家族，所言最上吉祥，現於人中受天勝福，此是虛妄。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝豈曾聞於人世中受天福者，斯為難信，所言於瞿曇法中當出家者，此說是實，以彼衣食因緣所逼切故，而後決定於瞿曇邊樂求出家。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所言斷諸煩惱證阿羅漢者，此是虛妄，以沙門瞿曇法中，決定無有斷諸煩惱，證聖果者。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時善賢長者，聞說是事，若虛若實，其心疑惑，即生愁惱，白外道言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我師聖者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其事云何？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今宜應當何所作？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」外道告言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長者當令汝子生後，於我教中出家修學，即能普學一切事業。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長者！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我雖此說，汝自籌量。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時彼外道作是言已，即出其舍。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，善賢長者靜在一處，審自思惟：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今一切不能顧惜而悉棄捨，宜設計謀壞所妊子。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是思惟已，善賢長者即持毒藥，塗摩妻腹。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，長者左邊摩藥，子轉右邊，右邊摩藥，子轉左邊，乃至遍腹，無處容受，塗摩毒藥，其妻以故，即趣命終。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善賢意謂：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「母既命終，子亦隨滅，而後無人壞我家族，亦復無人得證聖果。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時長者，既見其妻已趣命終，即時涕淚號泣。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隣人親屬，來相慰問善賢長者：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855a29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝妻何以忽然命終？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」長者報言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「因懷妊故，而忽命終。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b01_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」親屬隣人來相問已，各還自舍。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善賢長者即自思惟：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我妻已歿，勿置家中，可為施設諸所用物，送尸陀林。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是思惟已，即為備辦所用諸物，將欲出送。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隣人親屬知己，復來謂長者言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝妻已歿，不須啼泣徒自生惱。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，長者即取青、黃、赤白眾色衣服，及珍寶具，而為莊嚴，長者即時與諸親屬，圍繞出送，置尸陀林。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時先占相者，外道尼乾陀，知是事已，心大歡喜，即持幢蓋，嚴飾而行。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於王舍城，周遍巷陌四衢道中，告諸外道尼乾陀等言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝等知不？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門瞿曇先言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善賢長者妻當生子，其後生已，家族富盛，最上吉祥，現於人中受天勝福乃至最後，於我法中出家學道，斷諸煩惱，證阿羅漢。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』彼虛妄說，今善賢妻，已趣命終，子亦隨滅。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等當知，譬如大樹，根既斷壞，枝葉華果，其何能得？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸外道輩，相言告已，心皆歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸有清淨信者，當知佛世尊者法爾真實，無所不知，無所不見，無所不解，無所不了，起大悲心，普攝世間。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作一護念，施一無畏，已能圓滿止觀二行，已能成就三調伏事，已渡四流煩惱大海，已能安住四神足行，以四攝法，普攝眾生。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於長夜中，常念度脫，已能成就四無所畏，斷五分結，已出五趣，六法具足，六波羅蜜，悉皆圓滿，具足六種佛常行法，開七覺華，成八正果，成就三摩鉢底，九先行善，十力堅固，名稱普聞十方世界。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855b28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具足千種最勝自在，於日三時及夜三時，常以佛眼，觀察世間，正知見轉於眾生中，諸所施作。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處若有增？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處若有減？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處若煩惱？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處受極苦？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處若破壞？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處具有煩惱極苦破壞等事？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處施設少分方便？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處施設大方便力？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處施設諸方便事？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處眾生墮於惡趣？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處眾生得生天界？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處眾生得解脫果？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處眾生未種善根者？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令種善根。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處眾生已種善根者？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "使令成熟。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何處眾生已成熟者？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令得解脫。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛世尊者，具足如是功德，言無虛妄，離諸過失。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時世尊，審知時處因緣等事，知其所應放光明時，即從口中，出現青、黃、赤白眾色光明，其光周遍，上下照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光下照時，所有等活地獄，黑繩地獄、眾合地獄、號叫地獄、大號叫地獄、炎熱地獄、極炎熱地獄、阿鼻地獄，如是等八熱地獄，光明照已，悉變清涼。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有皰地獄、皰裂地獄、阿吒吒地獄、呵呵鑁地獄、虎虎鑁地獄、青蓮華地獄、紅蓮華地獄、大紅蓮華地獄，如是等八寒地獄，光明照已，悉變溫暖，以佛光明最勝因故。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其中眾生，蒙光照觸，身得離苦，心生適悅，各作是言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等以何罪因，墮在此中？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今日覩是希有光明。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」地獄眾生，發起如是清淨心時，世尊大悲，復於光中，現變化事。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸眾生，見所化已，又作是言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等今日見是變化希有等相，此處出已，應不復於惡趣受生，以佛光明最勝因緣故，身離苦惱，心生適悅。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是言已，各發最上清淨信心，彼地獄業，皆悉滅盡，即分人天二趣受生。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0855c29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "地獄眾生，由是真實，如應得利已，是佛光明，又復上照四大王天、忉利天、夜摩天、兜率天、化樂天、他化自在天、梵眾天、梵輔天、大梵天、少光天、無量光天、光音天、少淨天、無量淨天、遍淨天、無雲天、福生天、廣果天、無煩天、無熱天、善見天、善現天、色究竟天。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光明上照如是等天已，於其光中，演出無常苦空無我之聲，復於光中說伽陀曰：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「譬如大象沒泥中，　　以勇力故即能出，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛教勇猛大力故，　　能令生死軍摧壞。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此正法善調伏，　　所行遠離諸過失，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "息彼三界廣輪迴，　　滅盡眾生苦邊際。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時世尊所放光明，各各隨往，乃至遍照三千大千世界。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而佛世尊，雖放一光，其光收時，隨應各異：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊若欲說過去事，其光即當從佛後隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼未來世事，其光即當從佛前隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼地獄趣事，其光即從佛足心隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼傍生趣事，其光即從佛足面隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼餓鬼趣事，其光即從佛足指隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說於人趣中事，其光即當從佛膝隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼小轉輪王事，其光從佛左手心隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼大轉輪王事，其光從佛右手心隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼天趣中事，其光即當從佛臍隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼聲聞菩提，其光即當從佛口隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼緣覺菩提，其光即當從佛眉隱；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲說彼阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，其光從佛頂門而隱。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今佛世尊所放光明，遍照三千大千世界已，其光旋環，却從世尊口中而隱。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時尊者阿難，先侍佛邊，見此光明，即前合掌白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此種種妙色最上清淨光明，從佛口出，廣大照耀，普遍世界，以何因緣，其事如是？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語已，即說伽陀曰：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛於世間為最上，　　安住正因而真實，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "久已遠離二語言，　　斷除憍慢等過失。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世商佉及蓮藕，　　非無因故色自白，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來最勝人中尊，　　非無因故光明現。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來以自行願力，　　現證神通及大智，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀察聽者樂聞法，　　佛人中主欲敷演。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大智寂默大牛王，　　必說最上妙法語，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來清淨一音宣，　　眾生疑網皆除斷；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如大海及山王，　　若無因故不能動，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來正覺人中尊，　　無因不現光明相。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大智觀察因緣事，　　如應所作皆利益，",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨諸眾生所希望，　　故現如是光明相。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊告阿難言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是！",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難當知，如來、應供、正等正覺，若無因緣，不放光明。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今將欲詣尸陀林，汝可往告諸苾芻眾，謂言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如來將詣尸陀林中，汝諸苾芻發勤勇者，如應各各被袈裟衣，侍從如來，往尸陀林。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」是時，阿難受佛教勅，即詣諸苾芻所，到已作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛勅諸苾芻，如來將詣尸陀林中，汝諸苾芻發勤勇者，如應各各被袈裟衣，侍從如來，往尸陀林。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，尊者阿若憍陳如、馬勝、嚩澁波、大名、跋捺哩迦、舍利子、目乾連、迦葉、滿稱等，諸大聲聞眾，受佛勅已，即如常儀，被袈裟衣，來至佛所。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊與諸大眾，前後圍繞，詣尸陀林。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂善調伏者，調伏眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856b29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "解脫者，解脫眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "安隱者，安隱眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "律儀者，律儀眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應供者，應供眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離貪者，離貪眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c02_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙相端直者，妙相端直眾圍繞。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如牛王，牛眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如象王，象眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如師子王，眾獸圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼鵝王，鵝眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如金翅鳥王，金翅鳥眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如婆羅門，學眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如大醫王，求療者圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如勇猛將軍，眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如大富者，財寶圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如大商主，商眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如最上首者，多人眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如小國王，臣佐圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如轉輪王，千子圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如月天子，眾星圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如日天子，千光圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如持國天王，乾闥婆眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如增長天王，鳩盤茶眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如廣目天王，龍眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如多聞天王，夜叉眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如毘摩質多羅阿修羅王，阿修羅眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如帝釋天主，三十三天眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如大梵王，梵眾圍繞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如底彌囉，魚現大海中；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如靉靆雲將降大雨，周匝諸雲皆悉圍繞。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來諸根，調柔善順，威儀端儼，離缺失相，如大象王七支拄地平正圓滿，離諸過失。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來具足三十二相、八十隨好，殊妙莊嚴，清淨體相，無能勝者，圓光熾盛，廣大照耀，如千日中一光明現。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如寶山高顯而出，一切最勝，普遍賢善，十力四無所畏，三不護三念住，及大悲等，諸功德法，皆悉具足。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，復有無數諸苾芻眾，及無數百千人眾，周匝圍繞，隨佛行詣尸陀林中。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛所行時，有十八種法，而可稱讚。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等十八？",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無火怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c26_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二、無水怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三、無師子怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四、無虎怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c27_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五、無海難怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六、無他軍怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七、無賊盜怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八、無王難怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九、無惡人怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十、無關稅津渡道路等怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0856c29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十一、無人怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十二、無非人怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十三、無非時怖；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a01_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十四、天眼天耳如實見聞；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十五、施設光明廣大照耀；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十六、於法自在；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十七、於人自在；",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十八、無病惱等。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是善法，佛所行時，皆悉具足。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a04_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，復有無數百千天人，各各來集，隨從世尊，往尸陀林，觀佛世尊所應作事。",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說光明童子因緣經卷第一",
        "from": "T14n0549_001:0857a07_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]